<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62016890631ff37cfc40fd0533883d07384f953c","tid":1974151,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T16:20:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc9e701b57be0be0ff4e33cb8515d4bbcbf8ae18","tid":1974151,"uid":99644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T16:22:01.000Z","msg":"慘喇慘喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627e99a0ea6d94f08e35847690c2a4ff1b08dda4","tid":1974151,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T17:09:59.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5faead642d29c56bd8c414b2d8c9a7251e5dc28","tid":1974151,"uid":28020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T17:19:00.000Z","msg":"推呀！"},{"pid":"58f287898bbe60ad4cd2bcc8259502ef8726c990","tid":1974151,"uid":257351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T02:29:57.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"76464691872996d312276489cbc2278cca893b1d","tid":1974151,"uid":186882,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T04:03:53.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n<br />\n希望大家分析下<br />\n共產黨/共產主義只係一個名字<br />\n<br />\n真係恐怖既係有一群食物鏈頂層既人<br />\n為咗繼續賺人民幣去對支共惡行視而不見<br />\n甚至出錢出力去供養緊呢個邪惡軸心<br />\n<br />\n國際線比大家想像中難打得多<br />\n正如新疆，一日果個地方未變下一個新疆<br />\n其實都難以喚醒當地人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d7b5b9521e775e6a500c2503965b5e226d79f24","tid":1974151,"uid":175731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T04:16:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"414150d3512e3fad52614063f80eb89ff95ac9dc","tid":1974151,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T04:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3cb637056b2bde47ad4bf9ba3bc4fddb7936de3","tid":1974151,"uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T04:28:04.000Z","msg":"比班左膠害死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a8c434cb37067ca78f30bc9fcd2325b6d82d4e","tid":1974151,"uid":88294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T04:34:10.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"f0f8a22ba7d6097eea6dcc4efe2c5558ae9ee040","tid":1974151,"uid":34869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"df3a7b81b3f5c273d75af9ec9b908ffb7b951eaa","tid":1974151,"uid":154054,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:58:30.000Z","msg":"呢班人真係好撚煩<br />\n反trump還反trump 睇下個事實好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反到冇撚曬腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:17:25.000Z","msg":"果陣又話侵贏左會走離開美國<br />\n咪又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150a4f7785c9267512c2b3c00eaa82762745cc93","tid":1974151,"uid":216966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:43:17.000Z","msg":"lets link them up with 達賴喇嘛"},{"pid":"e4ad81be4c77f04ae2e95a4c85bae501a9eed160","tid":1974151,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T06:17:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"35e76f4c4a2964340d632c69ba75c5a7e4e5b3c0","tid":1974151,"uid":186882,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T06:25:28.000Z","msg":"再推<br />\n<br />\n大家睇清楚敵人已經唔單單係共產黨/支那人<br />\n歐洲奶共政府,甚至美國左膠已經聯合奶共戰線<br />\n歐洲政府姑息養奸，美國左膠（包括民主黨）包庇狂出支共fake news<br />\n而家國際戰線已經著哂火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歐洲線要由民眾層面反共<br />\n美國戰線已經無可避免地去揀共和黨，民主黨由揀china joe開始，已經無撚得救"},{"pid":"1c2993672998e439b1a6a0c66114dbee27b93a8c","tid":1974151,"uid":170865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T06:30:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9c4a0cec6e